{"tid":2262182,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"限枱六人 限聚四人 專家：無法解釋  陳肇始死撐風險不同","createTime":"2020-10-29T01:49:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T02:25:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6c3bc3cf8e299177aa42857023b52eb0c330dd5a","tid":2262182,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T01:49:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201029/VQ4V3B5THFHZRCCJ4FNQDEFW5Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201029%2FVQ4V3B5THFHZRCCJ4FNQDEFW5Y%2F&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KiudgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=957d4044\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201029%2FVQ4V3B5THFHZRCCJ4FNQDEFW5Y%2F&h=a8137221\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201029/VQ4V3B5THFHZRCCJ4FNQDEFW5Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n限枱六人 限聚四人 專家：無法解釋 <br />\n陳肇始死撐風險不同<br />\n<br />\n【自相矛盾】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：住戶中招 樂民新邨今派樣本樽<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】六人戴口罩一同前往食肆犯法，六人進入食肆後除口罩一起大吃大喝合法，六人飲飽食醉埋單後一起外出又犯法。富於中國法治特色的社交距離新措施明日生效，成為社會熱話。政府專家顧問認為限聚與限枱人數上限應該一致，但當局以「風險不同」為由堅持限聚比限枱重要。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7Y-bKD4BSlU5hjT7Muc5TPJOVn8=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JDPCGDDTDVFMFHCCUKW37YL5MA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7Y-bKD4BSlU5hjT7Muc5TPJOVn8%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJDPCGDDTDVFMFHCCUKW37YL5MA.jpg&h=a6dc4451&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■新社交措施明日生效，六人戴口罩在食肆外隨時違限聚令，但進入食肆後同枱就合法。<br />\n<br />\n明日起，餐飲業務處所（除酒吧或酒館外）內可同坐一桌的人數亦會由四人增加至六人，。。。。。。。。。。。，「入去六個就得，行返出嚟就變返四個？」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：217人疑因工染疫 僅1人獲賠<br />\n<br />\n許續說，雖然政府會與專家開會討論防疫措施，但通常只會討論放寬原則，至於放寬人數及執行細節與專家無關，他認為政府最新公佈的放寬措施不平衡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NhjnERSqsROx52BTrmzEjTrTZ-Q=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MXYK2YSNFFBVXNMZL4EVKO3LY4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNhjnERSqsROx52BTrmzEjTrTZ-Q%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMXYK2YSNFFBVXNMZL4EVKO3LY4.jpg&h=ac7d1d37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■港府將放寬措施，同坐一桌的人數由四人增加至六人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uWElP3rpXaavg7bfwxrAlQA6-m8=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TUZLIR443BAT7K2GAVL2GF66TI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuWElP3rpXaavg7bfwxrAlQA6-m8%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTUZLIR443BAT7K2GAVL2GF66TI.jpg&h=e9ca9edb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■陳肇始堅持新措施合理，「不能同一時間放寬所有嘢」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LVYYDTxNRhfqYMKOzHiPEPVBzH8=/1372x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2VURJLMRTVEJLFS3E3Q4LEZM44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLVYYDTxNRhfqYMKOzHiPEPVBzH8%3D%2F1372x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2VURJLMRTVEJLFS3E3Q4LEZM44.jpg&h=799f5e13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n何栢良<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱出於經濟考慮<br />\n<br />\n港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良在同一電台節目中表示，政府新一輪的放寬是自7月以來最大幅度的放寬，而政府放寬措施很多時候是出於經濟考慮，作出主觀判斷的行政決定。室內及戶外聚集人數不一致已有前科，在7月第三波疫潮爆發前，限聚令八人，但食肆則無上限，他相信除政府外，「其他人亦無法解釋」，至於解釋是否有說服力，則見仁見智。他勸喻政府必須向市民展示一個科學化「數字」作為放寬措施的理據，市民才會相信政府。<br />\n<br />\n對於外界批評放寬措施邏輯不一致，食衞局長陳肇始接受電台訪問時堅持己見，。。。。。。。。。，「今日唔調整，唔代表下一步不調整」。<br />\n<br />\n至於六人在食肆用膳後，是否需要分批離開，以免觸犯限聚令？。。。。。。。。。，「正常來說不會有問題」，但若不斷逗留在街上，就可能違反限聚令。<br />\n<br />\n實政圓桌立法會議員田北辰昨在社交媒體諷刺政府相關放寬措施是「神邏輯」，質疑「為何六人可除罩聚餐，四人戴罩在街上又唔得？」他續說：「有時政策落地，可唔可以用返KISS原則，Keep it simple, stupid，等普遍市民容易啲理解你做緊乜？」"},{"pid":"ebd0c798ccaeb869fc14399a1333835b89df48f2","tid":2262182,"uid":209890,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T01:53:57.000Z","msg":"六 四<br />\n明白晒"},{"pid":"a63ea4e1c6918737e83a7f920eee351299c11e7b","tid":2262182,"uid":82938,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T01:56:25.000Z","msg":"風險不同yes<br />\n但係食飯較商風險"},{"pid":"d6c59a5b1278d00692b893c03a4ab6265966bf1a","tid":2262182,"uid":187232,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T02:01:23.000Z","msg":"人哋問合唔合邏輯   佢就話講唔講道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正八婆臭西格"},{"pid":"d5baeb5a8e69c47e914d378fc2d39d6037aa9777","tid":2262182,"uid":259520,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T02:07:25.000Z","msg":"呢D擺明想屈罰款.<br />\n<br />\n6人店外等位.即犯限聚令.<br />\n有D店唔齊人,唔可以入,齊人就犯限聚令.<br />\n政府不如直接話,叫口號拉, 示威拉.<br />\n<br />\n你又要扮民主.真係小李老尾777."},{"pid":"dcd3f22a9f4bbdc586c63d6899a37d5c5063f82e","tid":2262182,"uid":169801,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T02:15:00.000Z","msg":"風險的確不同，但明顯係除罩食飯既風險大D<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"142d5bfe1f60783d361c01c967714bf9e012783f","tid":2262182,"uid":212168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T02:15:41.000Z","msg":"6個合法食完野出黎   行出去果一刻即犯限聚令<br />\n<br />\n要人前後腳走?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f08b53cbe9cf5d5083dffc276674fdf9ac76aacc","tid":2262182,"uid":72173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T02:16:09.000Z","msg":"依家d餐廳好有良心<br />\n有膠板仔當防左疫"},{"pid":"439a5f95191821b5f404582759aff5fc371a4492","tid":2262182,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebd0c798ccaeb869fc14399a1333835b89df48f2","tid":2262182,"uid":209890,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T01:53:57.000Z","msg":"六 四<br />\n明白晒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T02:23:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"314f542d7f7fda6a58c81ce2cbb0b436f215eb7e","tid":2262182,"uid":159876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6c59a5b1278d00692b893c03a4ab6265966bf1a","tid":2262182,"uid":187232,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T02:01:23.000Z","msg":"人哋問合唔合邏輯   佢就話講唔講道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正八婆臭西格"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T02:25:39.000Z","msg":"岩，佢邏輯都好有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}